### Users api routes


### Get user by ID
GET http://localhost:8000/users/3 HTTP/1.1


### Create new user
POST http://localhost:8000/users/ HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "aitor",
  "email": "aitor@example.com",
  "password": "123456"
}


### User login
POST http://localhost:8000/users/login HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "aitor",
  "password": "123456"
}
